WEBVTT

02:01:25.566 --> 02:01:28.191
we cannot arrest them without
first serving a 41A notice.

02:01:29.108 --> 02:01:30.816
How did he manage to get
such an order?

02:01:30.899 --> 02:01:32.816
Chances are, he requested
it from the court

02:01:32.816 --> 02:01:34.649
when the anticipatory bail
was disposed of.
